Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.15,0:00:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法 這個童話故事的產物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.99,0:00:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在21世紀早期 作為現實的技術具體化出來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.65,0:00:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在2030年前後爆發的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.15,0:00:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伴隨著氣溫急劇下降 糧食不足加劇惡化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圍繞著能源資源的爭奪不斷發生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.73,0:00:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在2045年 爆發了持續20年的第3次世界大戰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.08,0:00:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人口急減到30億人以下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.63,0:00:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這場戰爭之所以沒成為熱核戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.59,0:00:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為全世界的魔法師團結一致的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.95,0:00:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後到21世紀末
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.75,0:00:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在不穩定的情勢下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.46,0:00:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各國開始爭先培養魔法師了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,化身為魔神 兄長大人踏上了戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅僅只是為了我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底要怎麼報答兄長大人才好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.46,0:01:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要回報什麼才好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.95,0:01:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就連我如今的生命也是兄長大人給予的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.35,0:01:51.35,Comment,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.35,0:01:54.64,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,入學式的綵排馬上就要開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.02,0:01:58.76,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,請相關人員到禮堂…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全無法認同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.19,0:02:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼兄長大人是替補生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.38,0:02:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入學測試的成績 兄長大人明明是第一名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.40,0:02:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來不應該由我 是由兄長大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.64,0:02:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.41,0:02:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡比起筆試 還是魔法實技更為重要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是替補 我居然能考上一高…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.38,0:02:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要說這種沒有霸氣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論學習還是體術 明明沒有人能勝過你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是魔法 兄長大人要是用全力…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.52,0:02:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是說出來那也無濟於事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實在非常抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.32,0:02:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你代替我生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有這份心意我非常高興
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.59,0:02:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都是被你所救贖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長大人一直都在譴責我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.06,0:03:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有騙人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像你為我著想那樣 我也一直把你放在心裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.05,0:03:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長大人 你這樣說「放在心裡什麼的」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺她好像有點誤會了 不過算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪 即使你辭退新生致詞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身為二科生的我也不可能代替你被選上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.82,0:03:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聰慧的你應該能明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有啊 深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我這個沒用哥哥看看可愛妹妹的風光模樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長大人並不是什麼沒用的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 我剛才講出那麼任性的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長大人 請欣賞我的表現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.32,0:04:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 接下來要怎樣消磨時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,國立魔法大學附屬高中第一高中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是為了培養魔法技能師的國策機關
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能考上這所高中 也就說明是在魔法上得到證明的菁英
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是在這所高中裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說那個人不是雜草嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(512,437)\fs21}Weed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然這麼早就來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是替補 還這麼有幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是新生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什麼需要我幫忙的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.63,0:04:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一科生的學姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,CAD
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.38,0:04:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 我是學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫七草真由美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,數字的七 花草的草
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多多指教~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,含數家系…而且還是七草啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.67,0:05:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫…不 本人叫司波達也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司波達也學弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 原來你就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.35,0:05:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會長！綵排要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們談話中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前面一半是花冠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(497,437)\fs21}Bloom
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後面一半是雜草
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(497,437)\fs21}Weed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差別意識最為強烈的 就是受到差別對待的人嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.39,0:06:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你旁邊有人坐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請坐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…我叫柴田美月
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.64,0:06:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶眼鏡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫司波達也 我才是請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是千葉艾莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多多指教 司波同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.11,0:06:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這真的可以說是一個有趣的巧合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼巧合？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 司波 柴田 千葉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是有點諧音的感覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:44.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千葉嗎 又是含數家系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:49.19,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 真虧你能察覺到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司波 柴田 千葉 司波 柴田 千葉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼現在國立魔法大學附屬高中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:06:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一高中入學式開始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.77,0:07:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著新生致詞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新生代表 司波深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在柔和的陽光沐浴下 新生的櫻花漫天飛舞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在蓓蕾初綻春天裡的果實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能就讀名門國立魔法大學附屬高中 第一高中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感到非常喜悅 還倍受光榮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我代表所有新生 懷著作為第一高中一員的榮譽…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司波同學 接下來要不要去看一下教室？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我和妹妹有約了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:07:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個你的妹妹難道是新生代表的司波深雪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.24,0:08:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你們是雙胞胎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.31,0:08:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然經常會被問 但不是雙胞胎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是4月出生 妹妹是3月出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 你居然能知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 與其說是氣氛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:25.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如說你們兩位散發出的氛圍非常相似
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個女生 果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.14,0:08:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然能看出氛圍 你真有一雙好眼睛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靈子放射光過敏症
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再被繼續看下去很危險 我的秘密會…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.06,0:08:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.39,0:08:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.89,0:08:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中午好 又見面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 兄長大人 你馬上就要去約會了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能會這樣啊 深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:12.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這兩位是我的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這種說法非常失禮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.38,0:09:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次見面 我叫司波深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫柴田美月 我才是請你多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是千葉艾莉卡 叫我艾莉卡就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以叫你深雪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.56,0:09:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.79,0:09:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪你其實是很直爽的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪 學生會各位的要事已經完成了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天只是想打聲招呼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會長！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪學妹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,細節就改天再談吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:09:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司波學弟也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改天一定要好好談談
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會長！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長大人十分抱歉 都是因為我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.19,0:10:24.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你並不需要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.28,0:10:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 兩位…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長大人 我現在幫你沖咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.82,0:10:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:10:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方才那些人打電話過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說了些祝賀入學的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.01,0:11:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是父親和小百合小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是他們有對兄長大人說什麼嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.64,0:11:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是一如既往什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果連一封郵件都沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.66,0:11:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一時失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是無視爸爸要我去公司幫忙的命令決定升學的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這當作是器重我 你就不會生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長大人這樣說的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師 請你不要隱藏氣息潛行過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰讓我是潛行者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.07,0:12:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隱藏氣息對我來說就是天性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在已經沒有忍者這種職業了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:13:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是忍者　
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是繼承了血統的潛行者 忍術使用者哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.83,0:13:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道老師您是歷史悠久古式魔法的正統繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是您也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這是第一高中的校服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 昨天就是入學式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們今天是來向您報告我們入學的消息的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嶄新的校服洋溢著清純的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.11,0:13:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秀麗的外表下難以掩蓋內部的美色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老 老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直就是含苞待放的花蕾 剛剛萌發的新芽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 這就是萌 這簡直太萌了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅 深雪感到有些畏懼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您能冷靜一點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯嘛 達也 居然背後襲擊我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定光憑體術我已經不及達也你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長大人 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了 讓你的裙子沾上泥土了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 請不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連我的衣服都整理了 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種小事不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這個 兄長大人要吃早飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師您如果不介意的話也請嚐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司波同學你在做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在確認課程和註冊聽課
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速度好快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我只是很驚訝現在還有只用鍵盤輸入的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果習慣的話這樣反而更快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:02.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫西城雷歐赫特 叫我雷歐就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅長的是收束系的硬化魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.53,0:16:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫司波達也 叫我達也就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:11.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 達也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.54,0:16:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢 你擅長什麼魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.01,0:16:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不擅長實際操作 我的目標是做一個魔法工程技師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.19,0:16:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 你確實看起來腦袋不錯的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 司波同學你打算做魔法工程技師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,達也 這傢伙是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.26,0:16:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就叫人「這傢伙」 真是個失禮的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不招人喜歡的男生就是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.94,0:16:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 失禮的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別以為臉長得還算不錯就可以隨便亂說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外表可是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:40.52,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你這種把邋遢當成奔放的噁心男生是不會懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.68,0:16:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷歐 算了吧 打預備鈴了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉卡你也說得有點過分了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.48,0:17:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼老師會來…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,參觀工作室還真是有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的目標也是魔法工程技師 真是學到了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實很有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼複雜的工作我行不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定沒戲的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼 話說你跟我們一起吃飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在跟美月還有達也同學一起吃飯而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以跟你們一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.61,0:17:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪 這邊有位子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 艾莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 這是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司波深雪 是我妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次見面 我叫司波…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.51,0:17:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司波同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我們一起去寬敞點的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.85,0:17:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾他們多不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:18:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了 我就在這裡就行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司波同學 最好別跟雜草坐在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(486,437)\fs21}Weed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.99,0:18:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一科和二科最好劃清界限哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.74,0:18:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.89,0:18:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪 我已經先吃完了就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.07,0:18:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 達也 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,達也同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.39,0:18:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也差不多也該放棄了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.62,0:18:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們有事找她商量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:38.77,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,就是 我們只是想打擾她一會而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不必為此道歉 深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.23,0:18:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 深雪同學說過要跟她哥哥一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.49,0:18:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們有什麼權利拆散他們呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.74,0:18:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美月在說什麼呢 瞎誤會什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪 你緊張什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我沒有緊張哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 你為什麼突然用疑問句式？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.98,0:19:06.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們1-A之間的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雜草別插嘴我們花冠的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(291,437)\fs21}Weed
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(498,437)\fs21}Bloom
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不都是新生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這些花冠現在能比我們優秀多少呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(306,437)\fs21}Bloom
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.90,0:19:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.61,0:19:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想知道我們有多優秀嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.05,0:19:29.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還請你一定展示給我們看看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 那就展示給你們看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.27,0:19:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是才能的差距！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種距離還是體術比較快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.04,0:20:02.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我也這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.96,0:20:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你剛才連我的手也打算一起打下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.71,0:20:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼會那麼做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別打算敷衍過去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過是些雜草
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(481,437)\fs21}Weed
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.91,0:20:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.77,0:20:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.05,0:20:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗香？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.03,0:20:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 自衛目的之外的對人魔法攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在違反校規之前已經違反法律了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是風紀委員會委員長渡邊摩利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請告訴我相關事宜 你們全部跟我走一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.56,0:20:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的小玩笑開得太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小玩笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我們聽說森崎家的「迅發」很有名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了以後的學習打算讓他給我們演示看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們逼得太緊 不自覺就出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.94,0:21:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼這個女生想要做出攻擊性魔法又怎麼解釋？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.89,0:21:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是個閃光魔法 而且還抑制了很多威力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來你能分析展開的魔法啟動式嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.24,0:21:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太擅長實際操作 但是很擅長分析
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.17,0:21:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像也很擅長掩飾嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼敢掩飾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.56,0:21:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只不過是個二科生而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,國立魔法大學附屬高中第一高中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.21,0:21:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能考上這所高中 也就說明是在魔法上得到證明的菁英
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.59,0:21:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是在這所高中裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從入學開始 就已經存在優等生和劣等生了
